statements: SELECT * FROM community_engagement;
SELECT initiative_name, description, start_date FROM community_engagement;
SELECT initiative_id, coordinator_name, budget FROM community_engagement ORDER BY budget DESC;
SELECT * FROM community_engagement WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01' AND end_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT initiative_name, start_date, end_date FROM community_engagement WHERE coordinator_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT * FROM community_engagement WHERE start_date > '2021-01-01' AND budget > 5000 ORDER BY initiative_name ASC
SELECT initiative_name, description, budget FROM community_engagement WHERE coordinator_name IS NOT NULL ORDER BY budget DESC
SELECT initiative_name, start_date, end_date FROM community_engagement WHERE budget BETWEEN 1000 AND 5000 ORDER BY initiative_id
SELECT * FROM community_engagement WHERE description LIKE '%volunteer%' ORDER BY start_date DESC
SELECT initiative_name, coordinator_name, budget FROM community_engagement WHERE start_date <= '2021-12-31' AND budget < 3000 ORDER BY coordinator_name ASC
SELECT * FROM community_engagement_initiatives;
SELECT initiative_name, description FROM community_engagement_initiatives ORDER BY initiative_id DESC;
SELECT initiative_id, initiative_name, start_date, status FROM community_engagement_initiatives WHERE status IN ('Planned', 'In Progress');
SELECT * FROM stakeholder_feedback WHERE rating >= 4 ORDER BY submission_date DESC;
SELECT initiative_name, target_audience, status FROM community_engagement_initiatives WHERE target_audience LIKE '%Local%' ORDER BY initiative_name ASC;
SELECT initiative_name, description, start_date FROM community_engagement_initiatives;
SELECT * FROM community_engagement_initiatives ORDER BY start_date DESC, initiative_name ASC;
SELECT initiative_name, target_audience FROM community_engagement_initiatives WHERE status = 'Planned';
SELECT initiative_id, feedback_text, rating FROM stakeholder_feedback WHERE rating > 3;
SELECT initiative_name, submission_date FROM community_engagement_initiatives JOIN stakeholder_feedback ON community_engagement_initiatives.initiative_id = stakeholder_feedback.initiative_id;

SELECT * FROM community_engagement;
SELECT initiative_name, start_date, end_date FROM community_engagement;
SELECT initiative_name, description FROM community_engagement WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT stakeholder_name, organization, email FROM stakeholders ORDER BY stakeholder_name DESC;

SELECT initiative_name, progress_status, progress_update FROM community_engagement JOIN initiatives_progress ON community_engagement.initiative_id = initiatives_progress.initiative_id WHERE progress_status = 'In Progress';
SELECT * FROM community_engagement;
SELECT initiative_name, description, start_date FROM community_engagement WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY start_date DESC;

SELECT init.initiative_name, stake.stakeholder_name, progress.progress_status FROM community_engagement AS init JOIN initiatives_progress AS progress ON init.initiative_id = progress.initiative_id JOIN stakeholders AS stake ON progress.stakeholder_id = stake.stakeholder_id WHERE stake.organization = 'ABC Inc.';
SELECT feedback.feedback_id, feedback_text, feedback_date FROM feedback WHERE initiative_id = 5 ORDER BY feedback_date DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT initiative_name, COUNT(progress_id) AS progress_count FROM community_engagement JOIN initiatives_progress ON community_engagement.initiative_id = initiatives_progress.initiative_id GROUP BY initiative_name HAVING progress_count > 5 ORDER BY progress_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM community_engagement_initiatives WHERE stakeholder_group = 'Community Members';
SELECT initiative_name, start_date, end_date FROM community_engagement_initiatives ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT initiative_name, description FROM community_engagement_initiatives WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01' AND end_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM initiatives_participants INNER JOIN stakeholders ON initiatives_participants.stakeholder_id = stakeholders.stakeholder_id;

SELECT initiative_name, feedback_date, feedback FROM community_engagement_initiatives INNER JOIN initiative_feedback ON community_engagement_initiatives.initiative_id = initiative_feedback.initiative_id WHERE feedback_date >= '2022-06-01';
SELECT * FROM community_engagement_initiatives WHERE initiative_id = 1;
SELECT initiative_name, description FROM community_engagement_initiatives ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT stakeholder_name, organization FROM stakeholders WHERE role = 'Supervisor';

SELECT participant_name, initiative_name, role FROM initiatives_participants INNER JOIN community_engagement_initiatives ON initiatives_participants.initiative_id = community_engagement_initiatives.initiative_id;
SELECT feedback_id, feedback_date, feedback FROM initiative_feedback WHERE feedback_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
